#800
stone bishop priest~
Bishop Stone~
An old priest is here listening to your concerns patiently.
~
One of the founding fathers of the Ehregiz fighting style, this old priest
now gladly spends his time tending to the needs of people who have lost
their way in life and is looking for guidance. Don't hesitate to heed to
his words of wisdom, for he is capable of performing miracles.
~
