#800
Centre of the Cathedral~
You stand at the middle of this dazzling cathedral. Taking note of the
sparkling crystal all over you, you see huzzling people quickly scrambling
they way through the busy corridors on their various businesses.
In the center of this room is a small altar where donations can be given
to those more needy than yourself as well as a bank where you can deposit
your money.
~
